scopecontent.p:
Series II. Progressive Labor Party records, 1962-1977, contains internal bulletins, letters and statements, reports, manuals, news clippings, a picket sign, political buttons, and party convention and discussion materials. It also contains printed ephemera such as fliers, leaflets, and pamphlets as well as issues/editions of PLP publications 
                     PL: Progressive Labor
                  , 1962-1970; 
                     Challenge / Desafio
                  , 1964-1977, 2016; 
                     Spark / Chispa
                  , 1966-1967; 
                     MLQ: Marxist-Leninist Quarterly
                  , circa 1964; 
                     World Revolution
                  , 1968-1970; and 
                     Monthly Supplement
                  , 1974.
